sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Plugin
    participant GW as AI-Gateway
    participant SS as Skill Server

    Note over P,GW: 连接阶段
    P->>GW: WS 连接 (AK/SK auth subprotocol)
    GW-->>P: 连接建立
    P->>GW: register
    GW-->>P: register_ok
    GW->>SS: agent_online

    Note over P,SS: 创建 Session
    SS->>GW: invoke(create_session, welinkSessionId)
    GW->>P: invoke(create_session, welinkSessionId)
    P->>P: SDK session.create()
    P->>GW: session_created(welinkSessionId, toolSessionId)
    GW->>SS: session_created(welinkSessionId, toolSessionId)

    Note over P,SS: 用户发消息
    SS->>GW: invoke(chat, {text, toolSessionId})
    GW->>P: invoke(chat, {text, toolSessionId})
    P->>P: SDK session.prompt()

    loop OpenCode 事件流
        P->>GW: tool_event(toolSessionId, event)
        GW->>SS: tool_event(toolSessionId, event)
    end

    P->>GW: tool_done(toolSessionId)
    GW->>SS: tool_done(toolSessionId)

    Note over P,SS: 断开连接
    P->>GW: WS 关闭
    GW->>SS: agent_offline
